HEADWORD: Noctuary
<hw>Noc"tu*a*ry</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>noctu</ets> by night.]</ety> <def>A record of what passes in the
night; a nightly journal; -- distinguished from
<contr>diary</contr>.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
